values: I haven't wrote in this thing for a long time. So what now? REVAMP! YAY! Redesign... renovate... you get the picture. And this thing will be awesome! because I will update! Right? RIGHT? Right...

OMG ALISSA IS BAAACK! =D I haven't updated for awhile. But I have an excuse. =P Internet explorer hasn't worked for me for like mooonths... so I couldn't update anything. -_______- Anyhow, here's the news...

I have to go to Summer Academic Camp again this year.... like last. Oh how fun. -____- It starts on June 28th and I have absolutely no clue when it ends. But okay... LoL.
I have a new website, runawaymaiden.com expired at the beginning of this month. So now I moved to peachiekeen.net still hosted by Mel. =D But now it isn't co-owned, Moonlit Creations is maintained by Kim. I think she's recruiting co-owners though. [thinks] I'm not sure... :/ [/thinks]

Umm... I can't really think of anything at the moment... so ok. =D
Yes, it's one of those annoying friends only journals. I'm sorry, but I don't want just anyone reading my thoughts. Only my friendses and I! Buah ha ha ha ha ha...

There is nothing new here. Nope, nada... my life is always a boring thing. Nothing ever goes on. Isn't the complaining lovely? Let me tell you. Since I have nothing in particular to say right now I think I'll leave. Yea... yea I'll do that. =P Thanks for taking your time reading what  posted that was really boring, which makes no sense whatsoever.
